## VNC / RDP Access

| Method | Target | Notes |
| --- | --- | --- |
| VNC | Mac Server (tyces-mac via Tailscale) | Used for UTM VM console access and OPNsense GUI |
| RDP | Kali Linux VM (192.168.20.20) | Direct RDP for GUI-based attack tools |

VNC and RDP sessions are initiated from the Alienware over Tailscale. No direct internet exposure.
